title: Week 5 Recap, Mega-Stars Get Injured, Big Ben Combusts (Football 10/08)
description:
Nick Kostos, Will Brinson, Pete Prisco and Jason La Canfora discuss everything Week 5 in the NFL had to offer, including a 5-pick performance by Big Ben against Jacksonville (1:31), another thrilling Packers-Cowboys affair and continued Aaron Rodgers' heroics (5:24), the Giants dropping to 0-5 and losing Odell Beckham Jr. (9:40), and the Rams falling short against Seattle (13:37). The guys also cover a pitiful matchup between the Browns and Jets (17:40), if the Raiders are in trouble (29:04), Cam Newton's second straight stellar performance, on the heels of a controversy-filled week (31:13), and where the Eagles fit into the NFC picture (33:28).
